2010", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC5890.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document is one of a collection that, together, describe the protocol and usage context for a revision of Internationalized Domain Names for Applications (IDNA), superseding the earlier version.  It describes the document collection and provides definitions and other material that are common to the set. [STANDARDS-TRACK]"];
